All done. Build passed cleanly and pushed to `main`. Here's what was built:

**Command Palette** (`src/components/CommandPalette.tsx`)
- Triggered via Cmd+K / Ctrl+K globally
- Fuzzy search across navigation (Dashboard, Portfolio, Settings, all stores), actions (New Chat, Upload, Risk Score), and search placeholders
- Keyboard navigation (Arrow Up/Down, Enter, Escape)
- Animated overlay + card (scale/fade 150ms)
- Shows shortcut badges on right side of commands

**Notification Center** (`src/components/NotificationCenter.tsx`)
- Bell icon with red unread count badge in all page headers (dashboard, location, settings, portfolio)
- Dropdown panel (380px) with notification list, type-specific icons (Calendar, Shield, FileText)
- Unread indicator via 3px emerald left border
- Mark individual or all as read
- Click navigates to relevant page

**API Routes** (`src/app/api/notifications/route.ts`)
- `GET` — fetch 20 most recent notifications for current user
- `PATCH` — mark one or all as read

**Keyboard Shortcuts** (in `src/components/ClientProviders.tsx`)
- Cmd/Ctrl+K — command palette
- Cmd/Ctrl+N — new chat (context-aware: uses current store if on location page)
- Cmd/Ctrl+U — upload document (context-aware)
- Escape — close palette/panels

**Database** (`supabase/migrations/009_notifications.sql`)
- `notifications` table with RLS policies, indexed on tenant_id + created_at
